<br>
The problem with the Force line of spells is that they are all or nothing and they have an interrupt built in.  That means they cause a tremendous amount of agro (due to the interrupt as well as the DD) and are often totally resisted.<br>
<br>
Resists agro just as much as a full hit, and sometimes I swear they agro more.  <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   Add in the fact that you're using your most damaging spell and that it also has an interrupt and you're going to draw agro with it more easily than with any of your other current spells.<br>
<br>
I know GMMS can be spendy (20pp at the vendor, I think), but to me it was well worth it as I used that spell as my mainline nuke till level 29.  It is a very effecient spell for its level, and will work with an Improved Damage 1 and Mana Preservation 1 item where your level 24 nuke won't.<br>
